title: Worst Date Wednesday: Red Flags Sprung On Me Minute Before
description: Patrice is a seasoned online dater and is pretty good at picking up on red flags.  She was talking to a guy that seemed like a good match but right as she rolled up to the date he said that he didn't actually have a place of his own, he was staying in a hotel.  She still decided to give him a chance but the red flags just kept rolling in...
